        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"281383\">Richard Feldman</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/304641-ideas/topic/Add.20mod.20to.20the.20builtins/near/397980957\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>so the idea would be to remove the current  mod/rem operations from builtins, as well as the <code>%</code> operator, and replace them all with:</p>\n<p><div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Elixir\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nc\">Num</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mod</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Num</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"nc\">Signed</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Unsigned</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Euclidean</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Num</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span>\n</code></pre></div><br>\n</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Looks like the summary</p>",
